name: The Damned
description: A collab map in the E2M5/E2M6/E2M7 vein which at least 2 or 3 other Doomworld members assisted on building with me so the distinct styles show. I did post on Wads & Mods with screens but I had no luck. Maybe someone in the comments below will.. The level was built in June 2011 but since it was completed, it sat on my hard drive as I forgot about it. Now I saw I've not uploaded it until now, I'd say it's about time I did.
